Description:
    Add a newsletter into the manifest and create template which will be used to write and design your newsletter

Example:
    rails generate maktoub:newsletter "This is my first Newsletter with Maktoub"


    This will prepend content into config/maktoub_newsletters.rb:

    This will create:
        app/views/maktoub/newsletters/UNIQUEID_this_is_my_first_newsletter_with_maktoub.html.erb

    This will create (only if given layout doesn't exist):
        app/views/layouts/maktoub/LAYOUT.html.erb
